Result 2: Specialized result: test2
SafeService executing: test3
Result 3: Safe result: test3

=== Test 2: Exception Narrowing ===
Testing exception narrowing:
DerivedService executing: runtime_fail
Caught narrowed RuntimeException: Derived runtime failure
SpecializedService executing: illegal
Caught narrowest IllegalArgumentException: Specialized illegal argument

=== Test 3: Safe Override ===
Testing safe override (no exceptions):
SafeService executing: always_succeeds
Safe execution: Safe result: always_succeeds

Covariant exception types test passed!
